          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULlLxn-RU0sSrWt5tobEticNH3d_t_bB5pp4smsXrjjUP09zNX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I had a fantastic experience with X-Ray Technologist Denyse Nichols on Thursday, October 31st. Denyse was training an intern during my visit, and I was truly impressed by her calm and confident guidance. She has such a beautiful, teachable spirit, effortlessly explaining and demonstrating techniques to the intern with ease. It was inspiring to witness her leadership in action\u2014it\u2019s a wonderful example of what mentorship should look like. Denyse, thank you for your patience, professionalism, and for answering my questions about my right knee. Keep shining and doing amazing work",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUN2blBUTXFnRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xfbee1c1f4e712354!3m1!1s2@1:CIHM0ogKEICAgICvnPTMqgE%7C%7C?hl=en",
