          "description": "I had FAI surgery yesterday on my hip.  The staff is friendly and organized. The locations is calm, and not overcrowded, so you really receive all the attention you need.  I never once felt unattended to.  I would recommend this location for outpatient procedures.\n\nThe only thing to keep in mind, is they will ask you to prepay your copay/deductible/co-insurance. If you cannot afford to do this, they have many options and plans that you can choose from.  I have a medical reimbursement plan, so I didn't not have to pay in advance.",
