          "description": "I had surgery to my ACL tear, I really liked the attention of the staff , everyone was very professional, the facilities were excellent, I had the help of the translator at all times, my first language is Spanish, I felt very safe and I understood everything. I really feel very happy and highly recommend these facilities. Excellent work by the NYU doctors, Dr. Spencer Stein and his team did an extraordinary job, thank you very much.",
